Package: TSENAT
Type: Package
Title: Tsallis Entropy Analysis Toolbox
Version: 0.99.0
Authors@R: person(given = "CristÃ³bal", family = "Gallardo", role = c("aut", "cre"), email = "gallardoalba@pm.me", comment=c(ORCID="0000-0002-5752-2155"))
Description: Tsallis entropy generalizes Shannon entropy with a parameter
    q that controls sensitivity to transcript abundance. This package allows the calculation 
    of Tsallis entropy for transcript-level expression data and differential analyses 
    between two sample conditions.
